ironmesh (1.0.8-1~repo1~ubuntu24.04.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Add remote media metadata and thumbnail import so nodes can serve gallery
    artifacts even when local chunks are incomplete.
  * Back off incomplete media cache retries instead of persisting permanent
    media generation failures for missing local chunks.
  * Limit autonomous post-write repair to changed replication subjects and fix
    the Linux FUSE cluster delete system test around explicit peer repair.
  * Roll the workspace release to 1.0.8.

